---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Frontend | HTML, CSS, Vanilla JavaScript |
| Backend | Python, Flask, Flask-CORS |
| Database | MySQL |
| Auth | Session-based login |

---

## ✨ Features

- ✅ User Registration & Login
- ✅ Session-based Authentication
- ✅ Create / Read / Update / Delete tasks
- ✅ Task status toggle (Pending → Done)
- ✅ Per-user task isolation
- ✅ Dark theme UI with animated background
- ✅ Responsive design

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
taskflow/
├── app.py          # Flask backend - all API routes
├── database.py     # MySQL connection config
├── database.sql    # Table creation + sample data
├── login.html      # Login & Register page
├── todo.html       # Main todo dashboard
├── requirements.txt
└── .gitignore
```

---

```

### Step 2 — Install dependencies
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### Step 3 — Setup MySQL database
```bash
# MySQL-ல login பண்ணு
mysql -u root -p

# Database create பண்ணு
CREATE DATABASE todo_app;

# SQL file run பண்ணு
source database.sql;
```

### Step 4 — Update database config
`database.py` file-ல உன்னோட MySQL password போடு:
```python
DB_CONFIG = {
    "host": "localhost",
    "user": "root",
    "password": "your_password_here",  # ← இங்க மாத்து
    "database": "todo_app"
}
```

### Step 5 — Run the app
```bash
python app.py
```

### Step 6 — Open in browser
```
http://localhost:5000
```

**Default login:** `admin` / `admin123`

---

## 🔌 API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/register` | New user create |
| POST | `/api/login` | User login |
| POST | `/api/logout` | Logout |
| GET | `/api/todos?user_id=1` | Get all todos |
| POST | `/api/todos` | Create todo |
| PUT | `/api/todos/:id` | Update todo |
| DELETE | `/api/todos/:id` | Delete todo |
| PATCH | `/api/todos/:id/status` | Toggle status |

